- @title = "For Students"

%h2
  Built By Students For Students
  %span.small
    (you don't have to be in school to be a student - you just have to be trying to learn)

%p
  All of the lessons on Upside Down Academy are created by students trying to make life
  easier for everyone else.

%p
  Just take what ever you are learning right now and think about how you would try
  and teach it to someone else. How would you make it a little less confusing or a
  little more fun to learn.

%p  
  Once you've got that figured out,
  = link_to("create a lesson >", new_lesson_path)
